    <section class="content-panel container">
      <h1>Simulation Center</h1>
      <p>Experience real-world drilling scenarios in our state-of-the-art simulation center. Our facility features advanced drilling simulators that provide hands-on experience in a safe, controlled environment. Each simulator is designed to replicate real drilling conditions and scenarios, allowing trainees to develop essential skills and confidence.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="simulator-section">
      <div class="simulator-container">
        <div class="simulator-row">
            <div class="simulator-content">
              <h2>NOV Amphion™ Simulator</h2>
              <div class="simulator-meta">
                <div><strong>Manufacturer:</strong> National Oilwell Varco (NOV)</div>
                <div><strong>Simulator type:</strong> Full-scale drilling control simulator</div>
                <div><strong>Operating system:</strong> Windows 10 (x64)</div>
              </div>
              <p class="simulator-summary">A high-end training system that replicates modern cyber chair rig controls (Amphion and HH) for realistic drilling and well control practice.</p>
              <ul class="simulator-features">
                <li>Full-scale drilling control interface</li>
                <li>Real-time drilling parameter monitoring</li>
                <li>Comprehensive scenario library</li>
                <li>Performance tracking and assessment</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          <div class="simulator-image">
            <img src="images/ds600.svg" alt="ds600" loading="lazy">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="simulator-row reverse">
          <div class="simulator-content">
            <h2>HONGHUA™ Control System Simulator</h2>
            <div class="simulator-meta">
              <div><strong>Manufacturer:</strong> Honghua</div>
              <div><strong>Simulator type:</strong> Integrated control system simulator</div>
              <div><strong>Operating system:</strong> Windows 10 (x64)</div>
            </div>
            <p class="simulator-summary">Train on the HONGHUA™ integrated drilling control system with our high-fidelity simulator. Ideal for operational skills, safety drills and system diagnostics practice.</p>
            <ul class="simulator-features">
              <li>Authentic control panel layout</li>
              <li>Multiple drilling operation modes</li>
              <li>Emergency scenario training</li>
              <li>Integrated system diagnostics</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="simulator-image">
            <img src="images/rig2.jpg" alt="HONGHUA™ Control System Simulator" loading="lazy">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="simulator-row">
          <div class="simulator-content">
            <h2>DrillSIM-6000 Well Control Simulator</h2>
            <div class="simulator-meta">
              <div><strong>Manufacturer:</strong> DrillSIM / Simulation vendor</div>
              <div><strong>Simulator type:</strong> Well control & 3D visualization simulator</div>
              <div><strong>Operating system:</strong> Windows Server / Windows 10 (varies by node)</div>
            </div>
            <p class="simulator-summary">Master well control procedures on our DrillSIM-6000 simulator. The system provides interactive 3D well visualisation and practical exercises to prepare trainees for IWCF and real-world operations.</p>
            <ul class="simulator-features">
              <li>Interactive 3D well visualization</li>
              <li>Pressure control exercises</li>
              <li>Kick detection and management</li>
              <li>IWCF certification preparation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="simulator-image">
            <img src="images/faq.svg" alt="DrillSIM-6000 Well Control Simulator" loading="lazy">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="simulator-row reverse">
          <div class="simulator-content">
            <h2>Stuck Pipe Simulator</h2>
            <div class="simulator-meta">
              <div><strong>Manufacturer:</strong> In-house / vendor-specific</div>
              <div><strong>Simulator type:</strong> Focused stuck-pipe mechanics simulator</div>
              <div><strong>Operating system:</strong> Windows 10 (x64)</div>
            </div>
            <p class="simulator-summary">Learn to identify, prevent and resolve stuck pipe situations using our specialized simulator. Trainees practice decision-making and corrective actions across a variety of realistic scenarios.</p>
            <ul class="simulator-features">
              <li>Real-time pipe mechanics simulation</li>
              <li>Various stuck pipe scenarios</li>
              <li>Preventive technique training</li>
              <li>Problem-solving exercises</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="simulator-image">
            <img src="images/faq1.svg" alt="Stuck Pipe Prevention Simulator" loading="lazy">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
